### ======================================================
### RESERVAESTUDIO - PASSWORD RESET / CHANGE PASSWORD
### ======================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@email = contato@rockvalley.com.br
@knownPassword = REPLACE_CURRENT_PASSWORD
@newPassword = NovaSenha123
@accessToken = REPLACE_ACCESS_TOKEN
@resetToken = REPLACE_RESET_TOKEN

### ------------------------------------------------------
### 1) Solicitar reset de senha (envio de token por e-mail)
### ------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}"
}

### ------------------------------------------------------
### 2) Resetar senha usando token recebido
### Observação: copie o token do e-mail e preencha @resetToken.
### ------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{resetToken}}",
  "newPassword": "{{newPassword}}"
}

### ------------------------------------------------------
### 3) Validar login com nova senha
### ------------------------------------------------------
### @name signinWithNewPassword
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{newPassword}}"
}

### ------------------------------------------------------
### 4) Trocar senha estando autenticado (change-password)
### Observação: use accessToken do login atual.
### ------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "{{newPassword}}",
  "newPassword": "{{knownPassword}}"
}

### ------------------------------------------------------
### 5) Cenário negativo: token inválido no reset (esperado 401/400)
### ------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "token-invalido",
  "newPassword": "OutraSenha123"
}
